precis:
Amendment (SCHEDULE No. 1029) to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS which sets a
Maximum Residue Limit on the amount of the insecticide "IMIDACLOPRID" that
can be detected on apples and in tomato paste and tomato puree.
